legs.start_address: 100 Universal City Plaza, Universal City, CA 91608, USA

steps.html_instructions:
Head north on Universal Studios Blvd
Pass by LA Fitness (on the left in 0.3 mi)
Turn left onto Cahuenga Blvd
Turn left to merge onto US-101 S
Keep right at the fork to stay on US-101 S
Merge onto I-5 S
Take exit 110B to merge onto Disneyland Dr toward Ball Rd
Turn left

Turn right
Destination will be on the left
